trans-unit.source: This module does not broadcast change events. This means that the minority of windows applications which can have their environment changed without restarting will not be notified and therefore will need restarting to pick up new environment settings.

trans-unit.source: This module does not broadcast change events. This means that the minority of windows applications which can have their environment changed without restarting will not be notified and therefore will need restarting to pick up new environment settings. User level environment variables will require the user to log out and in again before they become available.
trans-unit.target: Este módulo no transmite eventos de cambio.Esto significa que la minoría de las aplicaciones de Windows que pueden tener su entorno cambiado sin reiniciarse no serán notificadas y por lo tanto necesitarán reiniciarse para recoger los nuevos ajustes del entorno.Las variables de entorno a nivel de usuario requerirán que el usuario cierre la sesión y vuelva a entrar antes de que estén disponibles.

trans-unit.source: This module handles the saving and/or loading of rules. This is the same as the behaviour of the iptables-save and iptables-restore (or ip6tables-save and ip6tables-restore for IPv6) commands which this module uses internally.

trans-unit.source: This module identifies and ENI based on either the eni_id, a combination of private_ip_address and subnet_id, or a combination of instance_id and device_id. Any of these options will let you specify a particular ENI.
trans-unit.target: Este módulo identifica y ENI basan ya sea en el eni_id , una combinación de private_ip_address y subnet_id , o una combinación de instance_id y device_id . Cualquiera de estas opciones le permitirá especificar un ENI particular.

trans-unit.source: This module includes basic account management functionality. If you want to have more control over your ACME account, use the acme_account module and disable account management for this module using the modify_account option.
